{"tid":786947,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Nintendo Switch 歐美版《魔物獵人 XX》確定將透過更新支援繁簡體中文","createTime":"2018-08-20T09:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T10:09:11.000Z","uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9295a8463827f46c2a6e88dd1a348917af95c2f0","tid":786947,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"CAPCOM 亞洲官方粉絲專頁方才宣布，預定 8 月 28 日推出的人氣狩獵動作遊戲《魔物獵人（Monster Hunter）》系列 Nintendo Switch 新作《魔物獵人 世代 終極版（Monster Hunter Generations Ultimate）》，確定將於上市後 3 個月內透過更新追加繁簡體中文語系的支援。<br />\n<br />\n《魔物獵人 世代 終極版》是 2017 年 8 月在日本推出的《魔物獵人 XX Nintendo Switch 版》針對海外地區發行的版本。以 2017 年 3 月推出的 N3DS 版為基礎，配合 Nintendo Switch 主機的性能加以高解析度化，提供最高 1080p 的高解析度大畫面呈現。完整收錄《魔物獵人 X》內容並進一步擴充強化，追加新封面魔物、新狩獵風格、新狩技、新地圖、新據點與開放 G 級任務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/30/670d66c262f92cb2b9039f4ed711zgm5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F30%2F670d66c262f92cb2b9039f4ed711zgm5.JPG&h=dc2d7299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/167065.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F5%2F167065.html&d=LaYFzeWo0jmsFzezrbAsB%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=cb279ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/167065.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CAPCOMasia/posts/2060682457284003?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCAPCOMasia%2Fposts%2F2060682457284003%3F__tn__%3D-R&d=LaYFzeWo0jmsFzezrbAsB%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=d35561a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CAPCOMasia/posts/2060682457284003?__tn__=-R</a>"},{"pid":"d8e2c5ffa9a5b72400091396fc0dfd33a843c672","tid":786947,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"Mhw 同 mhxx有咩分別？"},{"pid":"5e84dcc1b5623bf9c243ed03c0c4b279ea8eff00","tid":786947,"uid":168525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"p